      "content": "wait, that's a bit confusing. u said 'centrist analyses' say it deepens inequality, but then u said the 'progressive' view is that it 'misfires'? i thought progressives usually argue that cutting capital gains is bad for inequality... so what's the actual consensus here? is there a standard economic view on this or is it all just debate?",
